{"tid":1948032,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇愚樂台手足會買世界第一靚女嘅photobook","createTime":"2020-03-28T16:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T19:43:21.000Z","uid":217211,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"29c20c6cf08d8b9c2c467118f737497e1eca4fc0","tid":1948032,"uid":217211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T16:37:33.000Z","msg":"有冇手足會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n子魚真係巧令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYes, I am Tzuyu. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cic8vsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcic8vsf.jpg&h=c5fc79ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1ZF50z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1ZF50z.jpg&h=70b94734&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVLVasg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVLVasg.jpg&h=82d50f34&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nTWICE 的官方 Twitter 日前公佈，《Yes, I am Tzuyu.》寫真集將會由即日起至到 3 月 31 日開始網上預售，4 月 27 日就會正式公開發售。在官方釋出的一段預告片中，可以看到子瑜換上了多套不同的造型，有慵懶感覺的毛衣 Look、有純潔的白色造型、亦有深藍色絲絨短裙 Look，展現出子瑜不同的風格和個性。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kHNet1rr_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3kHNet1rr_0&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJew%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=dfe51159\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3kHNet1rr_0</a><br />\n據知，《Yes, I am Tzuyu.》會以多角度拍攝出子瑜，營造出溫暖自然感覺，亦讓觀眾能彷如跟子瑜過著日常生活一樣，因此亦不少得有「男友視覺」照片的出現，子瑜甚至會躺在床上跟鏡頭互動呢！另外，這本寫真集將會有兩個封面可以選擇，亦會附上一套明信片。假如是子瑜粉絲的話，就不要錯過了！"},{"pid":"1182839540bc136a9fd8d3ef4fe7924d08fe4072","tid":1948032,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T16:40:3